      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Matthias Gemuh</b>\n</p><p><b>Matthias M. Gemuh</b>,<br />\na German former computer chess programmer, and author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engines <a href=\"/BigLion\" title=\"BigLion\">BigLion</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Taktix&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Taktix (page does not exist)\">Taktix</a>, the engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=ArcBishop&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ArcBishop (page does not exist)\">ArcBishop</a> for <a href=\"/Games#ChessVariants\" title=\"Games\">10x8 chess variants</a>, the <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">graphical chess user interface</a> <a href=\"/ChessGUI\" title=\"ChessGUI\">ChessGUI</a> and the tool <a href=\"/index.php?title=FindDraw&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"FindDraw (page does not exist)\">FindDraw</a> to detect <a href=\"/Draw\" title=\"Draw\">draws</a> in <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">PGN</a> files. On March 28, 2016, Matthias announced his retirement  from chess programming and the end of the ChessGUI project <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. He died on 28th September 2021<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthias_Gemuh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthias_Gemuh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=181281\">PONDER=ON and TableBases on 1 PC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 27, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a>,  <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=192813\">Chess Programming: \"lazy eval\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 11, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_Evaluation\" title=\"Lazy Evaluation\">Lazy Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=215566\">UCI2Wb by Odd Gunnar Malin</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 26, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI2WB\" title=\"UCI2WB\">UCI2WB</a>, <a href=\"/Wb2UCI\" title=\"Wb2UCI\">Wb2UCI</a>, <a href=\"/Odd_Gunnar_Malin\" title=\"Odd Gunnar Malin\">Odd Gunnar Malin</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=198563\">Branching Factor = q/p&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 23, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Branching_Factor\" title=\"Branching Factor\">Branching Factor</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=202931\">I want to SEE</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=202933\">Re: I want to SEE</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2001</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=206802\">No explosions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Search_Explosion\" title=\"Search Explosion\">Search Explosion</a>, <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=262764\">BigLion and Tournaments</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 31, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=342287\">QSearch() as PVS()&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthias_Gemuh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=426309\">why is Patriot 2.0 beta&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 16, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\">Fruit</a>, <a href=\"/Patriot\" title=\"Patriot\">Patriot</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=426427\">Re: why is Patriot 2.0 beta&#160;?</a> by <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 17, 2005</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=432238\">Temptation for Fabien: going commercial</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 20, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=459898\">Chess960: Arena castle vs X-FEN castle</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 05, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=464214\">Chess960 in Fritz9GUI and Winboard_frc</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 24, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=15017\">Strelka and source code experts</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 11, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Strelka\" title=\"Strelka\">Strelka</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?start=0&amp;t=27853\">How to place a chess piece on a bmp square&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthias_Gemuh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35931\">New Time Controls for WB</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 30, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a>, <a href=\"/ChessGUI\" title=\"ChessGUI\">ChessGUI</a>, <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40116\">... using Arena</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47099\">ChessGUI and Chess960</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47169\">Nostalgia</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 09, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50492\">ChessGUI 0.245f is available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/ChessGUI\" title=\"ChessGUI\">ChessGUI</a>, <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52975\">BigLion and his clan have moved</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 14, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthias_Gemuh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57222\">ChessGUI 0.245h</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 09, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59666\">no more ChessGUI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 28, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64003\">FEN - Flipper for Windows</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 17, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Color_Flipping\" title=\"Color Flipping\">Color Flipping</a>, <a href=\"/Forsyth-Edwards_Notation\" title=\"Forsyth-Edwards Notation\">FEN</a>, <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">EPD</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70774\">Matthias Gemuh's (ChessGUI and BigLion) sad situation</a> by <a href=\"/Graham_Banks\" title=\"Graham Banks\">Graham Banks</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 18, 2019 </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthias_Gemuh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chess.hylogic.de/\">BigLion Homepage</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matthias_Gemuh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div cla